Subject: Optimization of AES GCM/CTR modes for pre-E2Kv7 models
From: Alexander Troosh <trush@yandex.ru>


1) Test of raw speed of GCM and CTR modes:

for m in  aes-128-gcm aes-256-gcm aes-192-gcm \
          aes-128-ctr aes-256-ctr aes-192-ctr
do
  openssl speed -evp $m 2>/dev/null | tail -1
done

